Process Engineering Staff - PT Guntner Indonesia
Process Engineering Staff  -
Process Engineering Staff
Responsibilities
Periodically evaluate manufacturing operation against standards. Investigate deviations from standard and take necessary action to keep actual operation on the track. Develop manufacturing methods and standards, labor utilization standards, and cost analysis to promote efficient operation and facilities utilization of manufacturing processes.Review and recommend resources utilization according to lean principles and value added operation.Actively participated in new product and process development to establish optimum manufacturing processes.Perform new material development in cooperation with manufacturing personnel. Analyze development result and submit the result to related function. Requirements: Candidate must possess at least a Diploma degree in Engineering background from a reputable university with GPA min 2.75. Fresh graduate are welcome to applyPreferably have minimum 3 years of working experience in same positionFamiliar with Statistical Process Control, Lean Manufacture, DOE, and FMEAHaving good analytical skillsPreferably have basic knowledge in HVACPossess strong communication skills, problem solving, follow through actions and decisions with sense of urgency, punctuality and ready to work under pressure to meet deadlines and targets with sudden changes environment.Strong work commitment with the ability to work independently and be self driven.Proficient in English (spoken and written) and computer application literacy is a must.Willing to be posted within the factory area in Beji – Pasuruan East Java.  If you possess the above requirements, please send your application letter together with CV (In English) and recent photograph by stating the position code in the subject of the email no later than two weeks after this advertisement to:gi_jobs@rad.net.idFor more information about our company, please visit us atwww.guentner.de or www.guentner-asia.com Only short-listed candidates will be notified
